- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the dynamics of best response games on regular graphs, which involves analyzing the behavior of algorithms on graphs. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper investigates how the topology of the network affects the behavior of players, which is a topic within social and information networks. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity): The paper discusses the complexity of the dynamics of best response games on regular graphs with many strategies. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): The paper deals with models of networks of interacting players, which is a topic within multiagent systems.
